&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="reference internal" href="http://www.SoftDevTrain.com/posts/setting-up-new-ubuntu-workstation.html#install-filezilla" id="id13"&gt;Install Filezilla&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
