&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="reference internal" href="http://www.SoftDevTrain.com/posts/setting-up-new-ubuntu-workstation.html#set-up-nikola" id="id18"&gt;Set Up Nikola&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
